虹山寺的表演团体“学团V!VO”是什么？实时流式传输乐器练习以显示成长https://www.moguravr.com/nijisanji-vivo/  Mon, 13 May 2024 07:42:32 +0000 VTuberにじさんじ https://www.moguravr.com/?p=250971 <p> “Nijisanji”是由近150名VTuber组成的团体，他们利用自己的特长进行直播活动。其中，由Liver领衔的乐器表演组合“V!VO”目前备受关注。 “Gakudan V!VO”是铃木胜先生（Pi [...]</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/nijisanji-vivo/">虹山寺的表演团体“Gakudan V!VO”是什么？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上，<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/nijisanji-vivo/">实时播放乐器练习场景并显示成长</a>。</p> ; <p> “ <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nijisanji</a> ”是近 150 名 VTuber 发挥其特殊技能来播放视频的网站。其中，以Liver为首的乐器演奏组合<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/ViVO_info" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>V!VO”</strong></a><strong>目前</strong>备受瞩目。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.7jg262f4vhu-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.7jg262f4vhu-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.7jg262f4vhu-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.7jg262f4vhu-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.7jg262f4vhu-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> V!VO乐队由<a href="https://twitter.com/Darkness_Eater" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>铃木胜</strong></a>（钢琴）、 <a href="https://twitter.com/SerAph_DazZ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Seraph Dazzle Garden</strong></a> （小提琴）、 <a href="https://twitter.com/Eli_Conifer" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Ellie Conifer</strong></a> （长笛）、 <a href="https://twitter.com/tctt10_10" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Todo Ritsuden</strong></a> （长号）、 <a href="https://twitter.com/emma_august_" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Emma Ogust</strong></a> （大提琴）组成。最初，它是由铃木胜等人在虹山寺的Discord上招募成员并通过试镜选拔成员而形成的“虹山寺表演单元项目”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="会员公开试镜#Nijisanji表演单元项目" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XOrSHYJFadc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[#虹山寺表演单元项目]第一次见面&amp;线下练习会【铃木胜/六翼天使·戴兹花园/艾莉·康尼弗/东辰电/绘马★小贺人】" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/DZdn4GaR0As?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[我尝试玩3D一枪]热情的大陆/叶加濑太郎[铃木胜，六翼天使花园，艾莉·康尼弗/虹山寺]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gRlHEIx2sQ4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> （分组前与3人进行会议）</p><p>据透露，该单位本身并非由虹山寺管理和领导，而是肝脏的独立活动，由成员自行选择视觉效果并承担费用。虽然尚未确定是否会出现在虹山祭上，但他表达了登上舞台的热情。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[Band V!VO] 第一届✨ 线上练习会 [Nijisanji]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gMgX9obi1UQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-1024x563.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-1024x563.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-300x165.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-768x422.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-1536x844.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/86fa01c88292808e55c8b5864a6624fe-kix.i3jj1kcokuwx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="563" /></a></p><p> Band V!VO的特点是<strong>实时直播乐器练习场景</strong>。我们定期在会员的 YouTube 频道上直播练习并表演指定的歌曲。在第一次练习直播中，你可以感受到只有在网上才能找到的真实氛围，比如演出开始前的调音和紧张。</p><p>艾莉·康尼弗说：“我希望人们将其视为成长内容，他们可以从自己不擅长的事情开始，并享受看着自己逐渐进步的过程。”一旦他们的活动重回正轨，他们正在考虑让其他肝脏作为特邀嘉宾作为表演者进行合作或参与演唱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Tears Surprise Cover Dissolution GIG [佐佐木咲/六泉/赤羽洋子/椎名优香/虹山寺]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hi12ikDSZp4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> https://www.youtube.com/live/ukdxGDE7Jyo?si=zh0Bai9i7EYCCfSJ&amp;t=1327</p><p> Nijisanji此前曾创建过以肝脏为首的乐队，例如“Disbanded GIG”和“2 Oki Dotaka”。这些单元的魅力在于，不属于任何官方项目，而是通过亲自动手创作音乐的过程，作为可以感受到每个人的肝脏成长的内容而受到欢迎。</p><p> 《学团V!VO》刚刚开始，但我很期待看到今后它会成为什么样的单位。</p><p> （参考） <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L-19HVyFDtg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube Uni [#Nijisanji Performance Unit Project] 大量公告！单位名称是什么？...有标志吗？ [炽天使炫花园/虹山寺] 说明交付</a></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/nijisanji-vivo/">虹山寺的表演团体“Gakudan V!VO”是什么？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上，<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/nijisanji-vivo/">实时播放乐器练习场景并显示成长</a>。</p> ; 
